@startuml
title Data plane - detail

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

[InferenceService] as Inference
[Tensor contract validation] as TensorContract
[WorkerRuntime] as WorkerRuntime
[LoadedModel] as LoadedModel
[Worker IPC] as IPC
[Worker process] as WorkerProcess
[RuntimeAdapterFactory] as AdapterFactory
[ModelRuntimeAdapter] as RuntimeAdapter
[OnnxRuntimeAdapter] as Onnx
[OpenVinoRuntimeAdapter] as OpenVino

Inference --> TensorContract
Inference --> WorkerRuntime

WorkerRuntime --> LoadedModel
WorkerRuntime --> IPC
IPC --> WorkerProcess

WorkerProcess --> AdapterFactory
AdapterFactory --> RuntimeAdapter
RuntimeAdapter <|.. Onnx
RuntimeAdapter <|.. OpenVino

note right of WorkerRuntime
  Master side: owns loaded worker handles,
  CPU budget, IPC calls and restart handling.
end note

note right of WorkerProcess
  Worker side: owns the runtime session
  and executes tensor inference.
end note

@enduml
